1
00:01:30,890 --> 00:01:35,020
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,820 --> 00:01:39,500
[1998]

3
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,400
Son, look.

4
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:48,820
Anything you need?

5
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:51,910
There's a parent-teacher meeting tomorrow.

6
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:55,000
I can't take time off tomorrow.

7
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,930
Do you have time?

8
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,590
They'll dock my pay if I take time off.

9
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:58,590
What do you think?

10
00:01:59,430 --> 00:01:59,840
Son.

11
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:00,620
Look, look.

12
00:02:00,710 --> 00:02:02,040
Wu Song has reached Jingyang Ridge.

13
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,500
What's on Jingyang Ridge?

14
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:05,590
There's... A big tiger!

15
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:07,640
It'll bite you! Bite you!

16
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,680
Don't scare him.

17
00:02:09,550 --> 00:02:10,310
Your dad is just teasing you.

18
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,640
Look, there's no tiger.

19
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,910
Look, there's nothing here.

20
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:13,630
Look. Look.

21
00:02:13,750 --> 00:02:14,910
It hasn't come out yet. No.

22
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:15,800
He's going up.

23
00:02:16,070 --> 00:02:16,840
There's no tiger.

24
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,120
Wu Song is going up the mountain.

25
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,050
Jingyang Ridge.

26
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:19,680
He's gone.

27
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:41,460
[Episode 3]
[A Strange Home]

28
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:43,680
Am I supposed to

29
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,400
be inferior

30
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,030
just because of thugs like you

31
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,030
and those

32
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,300
malicious rumors?

33
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:48,840
Am I supposed to let someone like you

34
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,240
who spreads lies everywhere

35
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,360
continue doing evil,

36
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:51,870
while I,

37
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:53,150
a completely innocent victim,

38
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:54,630
have to cower and keep my head down?

39
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:56,030
-Why should I?
-Exactly.

40
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,630
-Well said!
-That's right.

41
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:58,400
This young lady

42
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,720
was slandered for no reason.

43
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,030
Of course she should
speak up for herself.

44
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:01,830
Yes, exactly.

45
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,240
What nonsense are you talking about?

46
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,100
I didn't really

47
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,280
take advantage of you back then, did I?

48
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,240
You didn't take advantage of her,

49
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,710
yet you dared accuse her of
being a loose woman?

50
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:10,150
You should be sent to the police station!

51
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,080
Take him away! Take him away!

52
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,800
-To the police station!
-To the police station!

53
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,260
You all heard that, right?

54
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:16,000
Zhang Erlai admitted it himself

55
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,470
that he tried to take advantage of me.

56
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,680
He was the one
spreading rumors everywhere.

57
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,150
Nothing happened between him and me!

58
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:21,260
Did everyone hear that?

59
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:22,120
Those were all your words!

60
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:24,360
May heaven strike down
whoever spreads rumors!

61
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,280
You bastard!

62
00:03:25,460 --> 00:03:27,120
Last time, I saw you had a few drinks

63
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,030
and started boasting to others

64
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:29,420
that you'd done that thing
with Xia Xiaolan.

65
00:03:29,420 --> 00:03:30,470
Did you say that or not?

66
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:31,810
See? He said it!

67
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,960
Take him to the police station!
Say no more.

68
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,079
It's not true!

69
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,710
To the police station!

70
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,800
You pervert!

71
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,840
Take him to the police station!

72
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:41,600
Take him to the police station!

73
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:43,610
Quickly, take him to the police station!

74
00:03:43,610 --> 00:03:44,360
To the police station!

75
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,520
The police are here!

76
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,970
That's Zhang Erlai.

77
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,910
That's Zhang Erlai, right?

78
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:49,470
Yes, that's him!

79
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:50,079
I'm not!

80
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,300
Still trying to deny it?

81
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:51,960
All the girls in this village

82
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,240
have been harassed by him.

83
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,120
Still trying to deny it?

84
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,870
That's Zhang Erlai.

85
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,130
Enough. Stop talking.

86
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:57,190
We received reports

87
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,560
that you've harassed multiple women

88
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,080
and are suspected of being involved in
several rape cases.

89
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,810
Come with me!

90
00:04:00,870 --> 00:04:01,770
Stop there! Stop there!

91
00:04:01,770 --> 00:04:03,000
Cuff him! Behave! Put the cuffs on!

92
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,750
Cuff him! Behave!

93
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:04,870
You've got the wrong person!

94
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:05,710
Move! Move!

95
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:13,910
Running away won't solve the problem.

96
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,150
The way to stop rumors

97
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,630
is to face them

98
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,730
and defeat them with the truth.

99
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,190
The police came so quickly.

100
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:29,590
You must have done a lot
these past few days.

101
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,520
Thank you.

102
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:32,909
It's nothing.

103
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,510
How did you know

104
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:40,770
he would be here today?

105
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:43,159
I've asked around about this Zhang Erlai.

106
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:44,630
He spends his days idly

107
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,510
wandering around the village,

108
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:46,770
and he's quite handsy.

109
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,070
Many girls

110
00:04:48,159 --> 00:04:49,720
have been taken advantage of by him,

111
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,120
but they don't dare speak up.

112
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,450
Someone had to stand up.

113
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,240
That's why I came.

114
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,600
By the way,

115
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,480
I need to thank you and Kang Wei.

116
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,360
I know that these past few days,

117
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,620
you've both done a lot.

118
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,930
Even without us two,

119
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,190
you've already thought of

120
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:04,920
a solution,

121
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:05,800
right?

122
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,000
It seems like

123
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,510
you don't need to rely on anyone.

124
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,110
You can do so much on your own.

125
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,510
I want to do even more.

126
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,250
Now that I've come here,

127
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,510
I want to live this life

128
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:18,370
to the fullest.

129
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:21,560
You're saying things

130
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,020
I don't understand again.

131
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,510
Ms. Xiaolan,

132
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,770
you're really mysterious.

133
00:05:28,460 --> 00:05:29,660
Yes, I am mysterious.

134
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:30,870
So don't think

135
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:32,470
you can easily figure me out.

136
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:39,480
Looks like I won't
make any money today again.

137
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,510
If one day,

138
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,110
you get to make a lot of money,

139
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:46,800
what will you do?

140
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:49,360
I'll buy a house,

141
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,430
buy a car,

142
00:05:51,070 --> 00:05:52,670
and reach the peak of my life.

143
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,560
The most important thing right now
is making money

144
00:05:57,560 --> 00:06:00,160
and paying back my living expenses
to my uncle.

145
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:01,630
It seems like

146
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,840
you have a good relationship
with your family.

147
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:08,070
I'm merely returning their favor.

148
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:10,120
It used to be my uncle's family of three

149
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,270
living in that small courtyard.

150
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,480
How comfortable they must have been
back then.

151
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,910
Now with my mom and I staying with them,

152
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:14,750
we're inevitably

153
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,010
causing them trouble.

154
00:06:16,230 --> 00:06:17,270
Even with family,

155
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,700
I don't want to owe anyone.

156
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:23,690
So as for others, I definitely don't want
to be indebted to them.

157
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,360
Comrade Xiaolan.

158
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,760
Have you always been

159
00:06:27,950 --> 00:06:29,750
keeping people at arm's length?

160
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,120
Or is it just me?

161
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:34,150
Is there something I'm not doing right?

162
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,390
Mr. Zhou.

163
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,460
You haven't done anything wrong.

164
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,600
It's just that

165
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,870
you really don't fit

166
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:44,159
into my life plans.

167
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,159
As you can see,

168
00:06:46,630 --> 00:06:47,510
my living situation

169
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:49,070
is already terrible enough.

170
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:49,830
Just trying to improve it

171
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,870
takes up so much of my time.

172
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:55,560
I really don't have more energy
to think about anything else.

173
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:57,560
I know we haven't known each other

174
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,360
for very long,

175
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,430
and we don't know much about each other.

176
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:01,160
But I believe

177
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,060
you're a brave person.

178
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:04,160
I hope

179
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:06,000
you won't close yourself off

180
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,330
because of some rumors.

181
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,400
You won't be stuck here forever.

182
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:10,950
I'll also keep trying

183
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:11,920
to earn

184
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,160
a place in your

185
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,090
life plans soon.

186
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,800
Whatever you say.

187
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,680
Comrade Xiaolan.

188
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,720
Comrade Xiaolan!

189
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:22,830
I came to see you today

190
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,870
not just to resolve Zhang Erlai's matter,

191
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:26,200
but also to say goodbye.

192
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:28,720
I received a telegram from the capital.

193
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,380
I've spent too much time here.

194
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:31,630
I must go back now.

195
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:32,480
However,

196
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:34,159
whenever I get the chance,

197
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,560
I'll come back to see you.

198
00:07:36,310 --> 00:07:37,120
You should focus on

199
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,190
your own affairs.

200
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,490
It's no trouble.

201
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,420
Stop following me.

202
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,600
I've arrived.

203
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:53,670
Oh, right.

204
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,040
This is a stun baton.

205
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,870
It can protect you when necessary.

206
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:00,400
Let me show you how to use it.

207
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:00,920
Look,

208
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,270
this is the safety.

209
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,600
Press it once to unlock.

210
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:05,430
And this is the switch.

211
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:06,430
Like this.

212
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:13,360
I didn't know they had

213
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,620
such sophisticated gadgets these days.

214
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:16,920
Stay safe.

215
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:17,870
Thank you.

216
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,140
No problem.

217
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,310
This is my address.

218
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,720
Can we be pen pals?

219
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:26,960
[Send Friend Request]

220
00:08:39,909 --> 00:08:40,909
I'll be going now.

221
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,080
Comrade Xiaolan.

222
00:08:42,179 --> 00:08:43,200
I wish you all the best.

223
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,730
Goodbye.

224
00:08:44,350 --> 00:08:44,880
Bye-bye.

225
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:50,180
Pen pals...

226
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:51,960
Remember to write to me.

227
00:09:09,170 --> 00:09:10,500
Friend request withdrawn.

228
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:10,990
[Friend Request]

229
00:09:10,850 --> 00:09:11,510
Never mind.

230
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:23,460
This...

231
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:24,390
Xiaolan, what did you just say

232
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,660
this dish is called again?

233
00:09:25,660 --> 00:09:28,000
It's called duck egg version of mock crab.

234
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,200
Mock crab?

235
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,670
I've never had real crabs before,

236
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,330
but this is really delicious.

237
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:33,910
Really good.

238
00:09:33,910 --> 00:09:35,390
Our Xiaolan always makes these

239
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,390
creative dishes.

240
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:39,120
Next time when we sell duck eggs,

241
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,750
make a plate of this for the customers
to try first.

242
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:42,670
This way, the eggs will sell better.

243
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:44,080
Letting them try for free?

244
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,480
Isn't that too generous?

245
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:46,750
No,

246
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,900
this is called a marketing strategy.

247
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,890
Don't worry, I'll calculate the costs.

248
00:09:50,890 --> 00:09:51,660
W-What strategy?

249
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:52,480
What does that mean?

250
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,120
Marketing strategy.

251
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:55,540
Never heard of that term.

252
00:09:56,910 --> 00:09:57,440
Eat more.

253
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,010
Xiaolan.

254
00:10:00,550 --> 00:10:02,750
Now that Zhang Erlai has been arrested,

255
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,440
he won't come looking for you again,
will he?

256
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,700
He won't. Don't worry.

257
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:07,190
We're all keeping an eye on him.

258
00:10:07,190 --> 00:10:08,190
He wouldn't dare.

259
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:11,280
Fengmei.

260
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,600
New Year is coming soon.

261
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,630
Hurry and buy some oil cakes.

262
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:15,090
The pigs need to fatten up.

263
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:19,900
Uncle Yong.

264
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,420
Auntie.

265
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,270
Chen Qing.

266
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,930
Are you on holiday?

267
00:10:23,930 --> 00:10:24,190
Yes.

268
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,000
Come in and have some food.

269
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,000
No need, I've already eaten.

270
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,750
I came to get Uncle Yong
to answer the phone.

271
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,360
The village committee called.

272
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:29,910
Who is it?

273
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:32,770
They said they need you
for bricklaying work.

274
00:10:34,660 --> 00:10:35,750
Coming, coming.

275
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:36,440
I'm coming.

276
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,620
Auntie, I'll be going now.

277
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:59,150
I'll close the door for you.

278
00:10:59,150 --> 00:10:59,790
Okay.

279
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,200
Come visit again.

280
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,200
Auntie.

281
00:11:07,570 --> 00:11:09,200
How long has Uncle been working

282
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,130
as a bricklayer?

283
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,530
For over half a year now.

284
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,000
You know what,

285
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,720
this job pays quite well.

286
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,940
See, that tricycle

287
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:17,150
you use to sell duck eggs,

288
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:18,150
and this bicycle—

289
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,360
all of these were bought by your uncle

290
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,550
after he started working

291
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:21,480
as a bricklayer.

292
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,580
Is bricklaying that profitable?

293
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:42,870
Here.

294
00:11:43,830 --> 00:11:45,560
It's cold at night. Put this on.

295
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:49,780
Sit with me.

296
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:03,150
Xiaolan,

297
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,670
you put away that alarm clock?

298
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,100
When it's dawn,

299
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,000
the sunlight wakes me up.

300
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,770
I don't need it anymore.

301
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:35,010
Xiaolan.

302
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:42,720
Xiaolan.

303
00:12:43,710 --> 00:12:44,600
Are you enjoying

304
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,660
our trip this time?

305
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,000
Yes.

306
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:48,630
Then how about we

307
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,550
come out every year? Would you like that?

308
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:51,080
Yes.

309
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,960
Where should we go next time,

310
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,160
Xiaolan? You decide.

311
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,120
I want to...

312
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:20,660
[In Surgery]

313
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,000
Miss, how are my parents?

314
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:32,510
Xiaolan.

315
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:32,910
I'm sorry.

316
00:13:32,910 --> 00:13:33,840
-You can't go in.
-I'm sorry.

317
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,370
Let's wait a little longer.

318
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:36,630
Xiaolan.

319
00:13:36,910 --> 00:13:39,030
Your parents are still being resuscitated
in there.

320
00:13:39,030 --> 00:13:39,760
Don't worry.

321
00:13:39,870 --> 00:13:40,670
It'll be okay.

322
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:42,080
They'll be out soon.

323
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:48,490
Doctor.

324
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:49,150
Doctor.

325
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:51,480
How are my sister and brother-in-law?

326
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,410
I'm truly sorry.

327
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:54,040
We did everything we could.

328
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:57,390
I want my mom and dad!

329
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,320
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

330
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,220
I want my mom and dad!

331
00:13:59,220 --> 00:13:59,980
Xiaolan!

332
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:02,360
I want my mom and dad!

333
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,000
Xiaolan!

334
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,440
Perhaps it's fate,

335
00:14:17,790 --> 00:14:19,850
or perhaps it's written in the stars.

336
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:22,750
Although I've come to

337
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:24,000
a strange place,

338
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,120
I've gained

339
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:28,440
a sense of family love

340
00:14:28,070 --> 00:14:33,440
♪ Watching the flowers fall, I, lonely,
ask the night sky ♪

341
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:30,030
that I never had before.

342
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:32,950
Since I can't leave here,

343
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,720
I'll just make the best

344
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:39,190
♪ Is spring hazy where you are? ♪

345
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,750
of whatever time I have.

346
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:45,940
♪ Time is upside down,
the seasons intertwine ♪

347
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:42,270
Mom.

348
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,120
When you were little,

349
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:53,190
♪ Fate seems to want us to stay silent ♪

350
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:49,370
you used to like to lean on my shoulder.

351
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:54,600
Mom.

352
00:14:54,480 --> 00:15:00,190
♪ Time is so stingy,
even memories are hard to keep ♪

353
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:02,840
I still like it now.

354
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:08,740
♪ But I still remember
our promises of love ♪

355
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,360
Alright.

356
00:15:09,490 --> 00:15:11,440
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

357
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,330
Then keep leaning on me.

358
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:15,850
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

359
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:18,690
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

360
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:19,720
Since I'm staying here,

361
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:23,450
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

362
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:22,640
I should live my life to the most.

363
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:27,760
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

364
00:15:27,780 --> 00:15:31,840
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

365
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:36,980
♪ Together, forever ♪

366
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,490
Xiaolan.

367
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:46,600
I've prepared some

368
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,510
dumplings and eggs for you.

369
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:49,040
-No need.
-Eat it on the way.

370
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:49,570
Here.

371
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,400
Be careful, alright?

372
00:15:53,630 --> 00:15:54,120
Okay.

373
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:55,170
Thanks, Mom.

374
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:55,790
I'm off.

375
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:57,750
Be careful.

376
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:02,910
Fen.

377
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:04,870
Where did she go

378
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:06,200
so early in the morning?

379
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:08,950
Xiaolan said she wanted to try her luck.

380
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,270
I wonder if business

381
00:16:10,270 --> 00:16:12,200
in the provincial capital is good.

382
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:14,850
Don't worry.

383
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:30,260
[Capital]

384
00:16:31,270 --> 00:16:31,720
Wei.

385
00:16:32,430 --> 00:16:33,030
Come here.

386
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:34,630
What's up?

387
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:38,200
Can you help me analyze something?

388
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,280
About Anqing.

389
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:44,360
You've come to the right person.

390
00:16:44,930 --> 00:16:45,320
Let me tell you.

391
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,750
Although I'm a year younger than you,

392
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,860
I started working earlier.

393
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:49,120
When it comes to social experience,

394
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,580
mine is richer than yours.

395
00:16:50,670 --> 00:16:51,240
Let me tell you.

396
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,390
When pursuing a girl,

397
00:16:52,390 --> 00:16:53,630
you can't be too direct.

398
00:16:53,630 --> 00:16:55,760
You need to figure out her needs

399
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:57,320
and then strike precisely.

400
00:16:58,790 --> 00:16:59,720
Her needs?

401
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,100
What does she need now?

402
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:02,840
Money?

403
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:06,220
You'll have to figure that out yourself.

404
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:08,960
When are we going to Anqing again?

405
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:10,069
From what you're saying,

406
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,069
it seems like we need to go there often.

407
00:17:11,069 --> 00:17:12,670
Think you're so clever, huh?

408
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:18,410
[Shangdu]

409
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,640
Even if I can't leave,

410
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,030
at the very least,

411
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:47,570
I should get myself to live in
a more familiar environment.

412
00:17:51,110 --> 00:17:52,910
If I want to make it into the city,

413
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,610
going to college is one way,

414
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:03,320
and getting rich by doing business
is another.

415
00:18:04,050 --> 00:18:05,770
With my current resources,

416
00:18:06,140 --> 00:18:07,400
[Agricultural products]

417
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:08,790
trading agricultural products
would be the most convenient.

418
00:18:08,790 --> 00:18:10,400
But I'm not a real farmer,

419
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,560
so I have no advantage there.

420
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:16,160
In terms of profit margins,

421
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:18,260
[Electronics]

422
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:18,350
the electronics business
is most profitable.

423
00:18:18,350 --> 00:18:21,210
But the costs are too high,
and quotas are required.

424
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,750
I don't stand a chance.

425
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:31,270
Come check it out!
New clothes from Longcheng!

426
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:34,400
Come take a look! New fashion!

427
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:35,480
Longcheng?

428
00:18:36,710 --> 00:18:37,430
Clothing?

429
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:38,720
[Clothing]

430
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,270
This I know well.

431
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:42,110
As long as I can save enough money
for inventory.

432
00:18:42,110 --> 00:18:42,590
Miss,

433
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:43,880
come in and check out our clothes.

434
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:45,340
They're all in new styles.

435
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,550
The cost of one trip to Longcheng

436
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:58,950
would be at least 40 or 50,

437
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,920
plus it takes a week round trip.

438
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:03,200
If I stock less than 600 worth

439
00:19:03,270 --> 00:19:04,410
and make less than 200 profit,

440
00:19:04,020 --> 00:19:05,730
[Travel Fee: 50 yuan, Duration: 7 days,
Cost: 600 yuan, Profit: 200 yuan]

441
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:06,290
then it's not worth doing.

442
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,500
After selling duck eggs for so many days,

443
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,300
I've only saved less than 100.

444
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,000
Where can I get

445
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,930
600 for capital?

446
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:16,750
See, that tricycle

447
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:17,920
you use to sell duck eggs,

448
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:18,920
and this bicycle—

449
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:20,070
all of these were bought by your uncle

450
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:21,470
after he started working

451
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:22,480
as a bricklayer.

452
00:19:23,690 --> 00:19:25,770
Is bricklaying that profitable?

453
00:19:28,550 --> 00:19:30,810
Something's not right about this uncle.

454
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:39,920
Auntie, what are oil cakes?

455
00:19:38,890 --> 00:19:40,040
[Shangdu Oil Refinery]

456
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:42,030
They're the waste material

457
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:43,310
left after pressing rapeseed oil.

458
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:44,480
Pigs love to eat them,

459
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:46,540
so every household needs to buy some.

460
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,590
My thinking was too rigid.

461
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:50,830
I only thought about
selling things to the city,

462
00:19:50,830 --> 00:19:52,560
never considered the reverse.

463
00:19:53,740 --> 00:19:55,110
Sir, turn left up ahead.

464
00:19:55,110 --> 00:19:55,720
Okay.

465
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:08,440
Tao!

466
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:09,750
Coming!

467
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:15,480
Come on, let's carry these inside.

468
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:16,210
What's this?

469
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:18,470
So many oil cakes?

470
00:20:18,830 --> 00:20:20,000
I happened to pass by the oil mill

471
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,160
and remembered about them.

472
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:21,880
The tractor was heading this way,

473
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:23,540
so I had them bring these back.

474
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,000
But we won't need

475
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,240
so many oil cakes.

476
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:29,000
I know.

477
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:31,640
Are you planning to
resell these oil cakes?

478
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:33,390
Well, you see,

479
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:35,200
isn't the competition of selling things

480
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:36,550
from the village to the city fierce?

481
00:20:36,550 --> 00:20:38,080
Then we'll do the opposite—

482
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:41,480
bringing city goods to sell
in the village.

483
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:42,680
And then,

484
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:44,550
I can use that tricycle

485
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:47,070
to transport 100-200 catties at once.

486
00:20:47,070 --> 00:20:48,920
That's an advantage others don't have.

487
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,920
I've realized you're truly

488
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,450
a natural businessperson.

489
00:20:52,590 --> 00:20:53,480
These oil cakes

490
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:56,180
are in short supply
for anyone raising pigs.

491
00:20:56,310 --> 00:20:58,100
It's troublesome to get them elsewhere,

492
00:20:58,100 --> 00:20:59,500
but you've brought so many back.

493
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:01,500
Everyone will be fighting for them.

494
00:21:04,070 --> 00:21:04,680
Auntie.

495
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:06,750
Let's keep some for ourselves.

496
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:07,720
Didn't Uncle say

497
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:09,550
we need to fatten up the pigs?

498
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:10,080
Xiaolan,

499
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,440
you're so thoughtful.

500
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:11,920
Let's carry them back.

501
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:12,310
Let me.

502
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:13,070
Let me do it.

503
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,610
I'll go get the cart.

504
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,400
Xiaolan.

505
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:26,440
Here.

506
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:28,410
Soak your feet.

507
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:30,510
It'll help you relax.

508
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:32,590
You brought so many

509
00:21:32,590 --> 00:21:34,120
oil cakes back by yourself.

510
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,100
Mom.

511
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:36,920
Keep this money for now.

512
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:38,440
We're lucky

513
00:21:38,510 --> 00:21:39,350
that Uncle

514
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:40,440
lent us his tricycle,

515
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:42,240
so we could sell these oil cakes.

516
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:44,200
I can transport 300 catties in one trip

517
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,660
and make 15 yuan each time.

518
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,330
This way, in a month,

519
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:49,510
I can complete
the initial capital accumulation.

520
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:50,480
We won't have to do

521
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,810
such hard work anymore.

522
00:21:51,910 --> 00:21:52,830
We can switch to businesses

523
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:53,960
with higher profits

524
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:56,090
and implement industrial upgrading.

525
00:21:57,270 --> 00:21:59,800
I don't understand
these terms you're using.

526
00:22:00,140 --> 00:22:01,340
All you need to know is

527
00:22:01,710 --> 00:22:03,430
that we'll have a better life.

528
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:06,170
I believe in you.

529
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:08,880
The two of us

530
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:11,200
will surely be able to live

531
00:22:12,030 --> 00:22:13,790
a stable life like before.

532
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:15,590
Like before?

533
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,270
Mom,

534
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:19,790
do you still want to go back
to the Xia family?

535
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:20,400
You think

536
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:21,270
that life from before

537
00:22:21,270 --> 00:22:22,480
was stable?

538
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:25,320
We need to look forward in life,

539
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:26,480
not backward.

540
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:27,480
Well,

541
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:28,720
Xiaolan.

542
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:32,270
I know you're still upset.

543
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:36,730
I didn't say anything about
going back to the Xia family.

544
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:38,840
Alright.

545
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:40,880
You keep this money for now.

546
00:22:41,030 --> 00:22:41,550
Come on,

547
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:44,210
soak your feet before the water gets cold.

548
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:05,510
Yong.

549
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:08,790
Rest early, alright?

550
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,780
Xiaolan must also be tired today.

551
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:12,400
Yong.

552
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,480
Don't you think Xiaolan

553
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,400
has changed

554
00:23:16,550 --> 00:23:17,840
since her head injury?

555
00:23:18,370 --> 00:23:19,400
She keeps saying things

556
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:20,530
I don't understand.

557
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,550
Like industry

558
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:23,030
and something called accu...

559
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:24,360
Accumulation and such.

560
00:23:25,310 --> 00:23:26,440
This can't be right.

561
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,720
Should I take her to the clinic tomorrow

562
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:29,510
and get her checked?

563
00:23:29,510 --> 00:23:30,790
What's there to check?

564
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:32,850
You're worrying for nothing.

565
00:23:32,850 --> 00:23:33,880
That kid is now walking

566
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:35,270
on the right path.

567
00:23:35,520 --> 00:23:36,270
And even if

568
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:37,660
you think her mind isn't working well,

569
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:39,250
she's still moving
in a positive direction.

570
00:23:39,250 --> 00:23:40,970
You're just overthinking it.

571
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,030
Really?

572
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:43,290
Everything's fine.

573
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:45,830
Should we tell Dajun

574
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,440
about her business venture?

575
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:49,700
Why tell him anything?

576
00:23:49,790 --> 00:23:51,640
That bastard doesn't deserve to know!

577
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:52,750
Something this serious had happened,

578
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:53,880
but did he ever care?

579
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:56,000
He doesn't even deserve to
be Xiaolan's father!

580
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:57,220
You're doing fine staying here with me.

581
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:59,240
Why keep thinking about the Xia family?

582
00:23:59,240 --> 00:24:01,240
But I can't stay here forever.

583
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:02,400
Yong.

584
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:05,240
A woman should follow her husband,
for better or worse.

585
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:07,040
I can't just never go back, can I?

586
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:08,400
Why not?

587
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:11,310
It's a new era now.

588
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:13,160
Not only is marriage a choice,

589
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,270
divorce is too.

590
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:18,510
Heard what the kid said?

591
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,240
Think about it. You two,

592
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,160
back in the Xia family,

593
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,400
almost lost your lives.

594
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,260
The kid has finally

595
00:24:23,260 --> 00:24:24,460
gotten her life back,

596
00:24:24,510 --> 00:24:26,000
and she wants a better life now.

597
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:27,600
Don't you dare hold her back.

598
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:35,790
Hurry up!

599
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,130
It's about to rain.

600
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:39,440
If this grain gets wet,

601
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:41,030
our whole year's work will be wasted!

602
00:24:41,030 --> 00:24:41,750
Hurry up!

603
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:42,680
Come on!

604
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,400
Hurry up!

605
00:24:50,360 --> 00:24:51,520
Quick, quick!

606
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:53,160
This weather is really working against us.

607
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,110
What's happening?

608
00:24:54,110 --> 00:24:55,590
It's about to rain! Collect the grain!

609
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:56,440
It's about to rain!

610
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:57,500
Collect the grain!

611
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,000
Hurry! Hurry!

612
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:07,200
Quick, get that!

613
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:07,680
Here.

614
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,130
Use this basket.

615
00:25:09,350 --> 00:25:10,310
Tao, be careful!

616
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,400
Come on, let's go!

617
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:13,680
Let's go!

618
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:14,770
Careful.

619
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:17,320
Let's go.

620
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:18,100
Come on.

621
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:19,030
Here.

622
00:25:23,160 --> 00:25:24,490
Put more effort into it!

623
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:26,210
Come on.

624
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:32,800
Give it to me.

625
00:25:37,110 --> 00:25:37,830
Come on.

626
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:38,640
Let's go.

627
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:39,550
Come on, let's go.

628
00:25:39,550 --> 00:25:40,200
Duck down.

629
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:40,930
Let's go.

630
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,510
Let's go.

631
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:44,790
Hurry up.

632
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:46,220
Let's go. Let's go.

633
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,580
Come on, put your back into it.

634
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,140
Come on!

635
00:25:57,240 --> 00:25:57,770
Hurry up!

636
00:25:58,550 --> 00:25:59,350
Hurry, hurry!

637
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:00,400
Quick, quick!

638
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,240
Careful. Careful.

639
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:01,750
Hurry!

640
00:26:02,550 --> 00:26:03,350
This rain.

641
00:26:04,590 --> 00:26:05,590
Look at this rain,

642
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:07,180
it's chasing after us!

643
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:10,700
Thanks to Fen and Xiaolan.

644
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:11,750
Otherwise, we

645
00:26:11,750 --> 00:26:13,080
couldn't have managed.

646
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:16,110
Come on. Have some water.

647
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:17,040
Have some water.

648
00:26:17,220 --> 00:26:18,080
I'm so thirsty.

649
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,330
My son is so capable.

650
00:26:22,510 --> 00:26:23,660
You can even help with the chores now.

651
00:26:23,660 --> 00:26:25,530
Get a towel. Look how wet it is.

652
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:29,530
Look at all this sweat.

653
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:31,160
Even I feel like

654
00:26:31,550 --> 00:26:33,350
I look like part of their family.

655
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:35,000
It seems

656
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,550
I've already adapted to this place

657
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:37,810
and adapted to the life

658
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:40,100
of becoming another Xia Xiaolan.

659
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:41,640
Xiaolan.

660
00:26:42,350 --> 00:26:43,200
Have some water. Here.

661
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,270
I worked hard today.

662
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:44,590
Good.

663
00:26:44,590 --> 00:26:45,400
What tasty food

664
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,510
can I have for dinner?

665
00:26:46,510 --> 00:26:47,480
I'll fry you a sunny-side-up egg.

666
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,140
How's that?

667
00:26:49,310 --> 00:26:51,400
One for you

668
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:52,610
and one for Xiaolan.

669
00:27:06,790 --> 00:27:08,200
After so many days of drought,

670
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,600
we finally got some rain.

671
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,740
That's wonderful.

672
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:12,240
This family

673
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:14,810
is always making a fuss over nothing.

674
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,680
Always in chaos.

675
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:19,680
Always in a flurry.

676
00:27:20,830 --> 00:27:21,360
Xiaolan,

677
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,170
what do you want for dinner?

678
00:27:26,070 --> 00:27:27,070
Anything's fine.

679
00:27:30,030 --> 00:27:31,010
I'll make her hand-pulled noodles.

680
00:27:31,010 --> 00:27:33,270
She loves hand-pulled noodles the most.

681
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:36,590
And there's some

682
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:39,650
warmth that I don't want to admit.

683
00:27:43,270 --> 00:27:45,550
Oh heavens!

684
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,070
Hurry!

685
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:48,070
Quick!

686
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:48,960
Hurry up!

687
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:51,480
Put it down!

688
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:54,400
This year's harvest!

689
00:27:55,120 --> 00:27:56,080
Hurry up!

690
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,510
Go quickly!

691
00:27:58,790 --> 00:28:00,850
Don't worry about that!

692
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:02,030
Go now!

693
00:28:03,110 --> 00:28:03,550
You...

694
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:06,170
Heavens, please stop raining!

695
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:08,400
Oh heavens, please stop!

696
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:09,350
Stop raining!

697
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:11,240
Please stop! My grain!

698
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:12,880
Dajun!

699
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,590
Dajun, hurry!

700
00:28:14,720 --> 00:28:16,030
Go collect the grain!

701
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:16,270
Okay!

702
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:18,160
The grain is all soaked!

703
00:28:18,240 --> 00:28:18,510
Alright.

704
00:28:18,510 --> 00:28:19,160
Hurry up!

705
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:19,590
Got it.

706
00:28:19,590 --> 00:28:20,550
Hurry!

707
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:23,510
Good heavens.

708
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:24,590
Let us collect

709
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:25,680
all the grain back, please!

710
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,790
Good heavens.

711
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:29,680
My poor grain.

712
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:30,830
Have some hot water.

713
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:32,240
Soaked by the rain like this.

714
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,590
Give me a drink quickly.
I'm dying of thirst.

715
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:34,650
Alright, alright.

716
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,810
Have some hot water.

717
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,000
Alright.

718
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:38,700
Seeing the millet soaked like this

719
00:28:38,700 --> 00:28:39,700
makes me so angry.

720
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:42,070
We're so busy in this household,

721
00:28:42,090 --> 00:28:43,400
yet those two ran off
to her parents' home.

722
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:45,270
They didn't even come back to check on us.

723
00:28:45,270 --> 00:28:47,470
As if they're not part of the Xia family.

724
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:49,410
I'm so thirsty.

725
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,000
Dajun,

726
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:52,240
tell me the truth today.

727
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:55,580
Are you going to continue that marriage
or what?

728
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,680
Those two, Liu Fen and her daughter,

729
00:28:57,680 --> 00:28:59,030
they really know how to avoid work.

730
00:28:59,030 --> 00:29:01,030
We're so busy on the farms right now,

731
00:29:01,420 --> 00:29:02,790
yet they've run off to her mother's home.

732
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:03,990
Mother, look at that.

733
00:29:06,960 --> 00:29:08,360
I'll bring them two back.

734
00:29:12,790 --> 00:29:14,350
A few days ago,

735
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:16,010
I ran into Xia Xiaolan in town.

736
00:29:16,200 --> 00:29:17,640
She seemed to be selling duck eggs.

737
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:19,550
And there was a man standing beside her.

738
00:29:19,550 --> 00:29:21,610
-Really?
-And he was quite handsome.

739
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,010
Hongxia.

740
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:24,590
Take Junshan and Junbao inside.

741
00:29:24,590 --> 00:29:26,270
What are you grinning about? Go inside.

742
00:29:26,270 --> 00:29:27,440
Go play inside. Go.

743
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:30,190
This room.

744
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:31,970
Mother.

745
00:29:32,470 --> 00:29:34,240
Hongxia is a very honest kid.

746
00:29:34,350 --> 00:29:35,380
She never lies.

747
00:29:35,720 --> 00:29:37,160
Who knows

748
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:39,110
what Xiaolan was actually doing there?

749
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:40,830
Luckily, it was Hongxia who saw her.

750
00:29:40,830 --> 00:29:42,430
If it had been an outsider...

751
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:46,320
Right?

752
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,740
Alright, alright.

753
00:29:47,790 --> 00:29:48,830
It's normal for family members

754
00:29:48,830 --> 00:29:50,030
to have disagreements.

755
00:29:50,030 --> 00:29:51,070
Let's have Xiaolan come back first

756
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:52,550
and apologize to her grandmother.

757
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:54,150
Then we can still be a family.

758
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:55,690
She acted

759
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:56,960
without thinking of the consequences.

760
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,960
Look how upset she made her grandma.

761
00:29:59,510 --> 00:30:02,240
It's okay that I got upset.

762
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:03,820
The main thing is that Ziyu

763
00:30:03,820 --> 00:30:05,060
has been wronged.

764
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:06,920
Ziyu is

765
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:08,000
being the bigger person.

766
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,400
That's because she's generous,

767
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:10,030
right?

768
00:30:11,790 --> 00:30:13,850
Tomorrow, I'll go to Qijing Village,

769
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:15,030
bring them back,

770
00:30:16,270 --> 00:30:18,110
and have Xiaolan write an apology letter
to Ziyu.

771
00:30:18,110 --> 00:30:19,590
If one isn't enough, then two.

772
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:20,110
Until

773
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:21,770
Ziyu forgives them.

774
00:30:24,310 --> 00:30:25,440
That's more like it.

775
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:28,070
Mother.

776
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:29,780
How about this?

777
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:30,550
Tomorrow,

778
00:30:30,550 --> 00:30:31,880
I'll go with Dajun.

779
00:30:32,430 --> 00:30:34,440
Men can be a bit too blunt when they talk.

780
00:30:34,440 --> 00:30:36,040
Let's not make things worse.

781
00:30:37,590 --> 00:30:38,120
Alright.

782
00:30:38,510 --> 00:30:38,970
Mother.

783
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,030
Then it's settled.

784
00:30:40,030 --> 00:30:41,270
I'll go with them.

785
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:43,480
This time, we'll bring Fen back

786
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:45,200
even if we have to carry her on the back.

787
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:45,730
Alright.

788
00:30:46,110 --> 00:30:46,640
Alright.

789
00:30:48,080 --> 00:30:48,790
She just won't leave me alone.

790
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:49,610
Now we just need

791
00:30:49,610 --> 00:30:51,800
to hope for the rain to stop

792
00:30:51,830 --> 00:30:53,290
and for the sun to come out.

793
00:30:58,400 --> 00:30:59,720
Can you count it properly?

794
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,920
If not, just go to bed.

795
00:31:01,270 --> 00:31:02,350
What do you know?

796
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:04,960
I'm arranging the money neatly.

797
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:06,660
Only when you treat money well

798
00:31:06,660 --> 00:31:08,120
will money treat you well.

799
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:10,270
Alright, tomorrow,

800
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:12,790
bring Xia Xiaolan back.

801
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:14,000
Ziyu is right.

802
00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:17,790
We'll only feel at ease
when she's right in front of us.

803
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:18,830
Get on with it.

804
00:31:22,590 --> 00:31:23,400
Don't sleep yet.

805
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:24,200
Listen.

806
00:31:24,590 --> 00:31:25,400
What if I get her

807
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,310
a husband?

808
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:27,740
Think about it.

809
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:29,750
Once she's married off,

810
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,180
it's settled for life.

811
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:34,680
She won't be able to
ruin our daughter's life anymore.

812
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,680
Have you lost your mind?

813
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:36,720
With her reputation,

814
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,850
who would marry her?

815
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:38,790
Finding a husband?

816
00:31:38,790 --> 00:31:39,640
If she could find a widower

817
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:40,400
or an old bachelor,

818
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:41,510
that would be a blessing already.

819
00:31:41,510 --> 00:31:42,440
You understand?

820
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:45,540
And you're talking about finding her
a husband.

821
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:46,750
Right.

822
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:48,270
I just thought of someone.

823
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:49,400
You startled me.

824
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:50,270
Who?

825
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:51,650
Zhang Erlai.

826
00:31:53,760 --> 00:31:54,760
Right!

827
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:56,750
If she gets together with Zhang Erlai,

828
00:31:56,750 --> 00:31:58,200
we'll even get some bride price.

829
00:31:58,200 --> 00:31:59,590
We can use it to support our Ziyu.

830
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:01,110
She'll need a lot of money in the capital,

831
00:32:01,110 --> 00:32:01,590
right?

832
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:04,270
I didn't think of that.

833
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:07,200
You're so clever.

834
00:32:07,600 --> 00:32:09,200
If she gets together with Zhang Erlai,

835
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:11,060
we'll have some bride price to...

836
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,730
Wait, that's not right.

837
00:32:13,960 --> 00:32:14,720
What now?

838
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:17,030
If she gets together with Zhang Erlai

839
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:18,510
and the note incident gets revealed,

840
00:32:18,510 --> 00:32:19,110
what then?

841
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,830
So what if it does?

842
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,770
What can she do about it?

843
00:32:22,890 --> 00:32:23,690
By that time,

844
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:24,830
even if she knows, what can she do?

845
00:32:24,830 --> 00:32:25,440
Tell me.

846
00:32:26,550 --> 00:32:29,410
Thinking about useless things all day.
Go to sleep.

847
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:30,960
That's right.

848
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,640
What can she possibly do?

849
00:32:34,030 --> 00:32:35,290
She can't do anything.

850
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:36,720
First thing tomorrow morning,

851
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:38,030
I'll go get her.

852
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:41,360
Bringing her back early
will save us trouble.

853
00:33:09,270 --> 00:33:10,870
I really can't walk anymore.

854
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:13,550
Can't you two slow down?

855
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:16,110
Hurry up, Sister-in-law.

856
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:18,000
We still need to get back today.

857
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:20,160
This village is all mountain paths.

858
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:21,960
I really can't walk anymore.

859
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,010
Isn't that Xia Xiaolan?

860
00:33:40,030 --> 00:33:40,960
How can you not greet your elders

861
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:41,960
-when you meet them?
-Xiaolan?

862
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:42,890
It really is her.

863
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,070
Xiaolan.

864
00:33:45,550 --> 00:33:46,790
We've come to get you.

865
00:33:47,610 --> 00:33:49,850
Seeing your father and aunts,

866
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,540
how can you not even say hello?

867
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:53,590
It seems

868
00:33:54,230 --> 00:33:55,890
this is Xia Xiaolan's father,

869
00:33:56,090 --> 00:33:57,000
Xia Dajun.

870
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:00,480
Xia Dajun, right?

871
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:04,970
She's calling you by your name.

872
00:34:05,690 --> 00:34:08,020
What are you doing here in Qijing Village?

873
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:09,630
You... How dare you talk to

874
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:10,550
me like that?

875
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:12,510
If it weren't for

876
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:13,510
my mother's sake,

877
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:14,620
I wouldn't even bother with you.

878
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:15,230
This kid...

879
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:16,230
Stop right there!

880
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:20,219
Let me tell you something.

881
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:21,929
Don't start a fight.

882
00:34:21,929 --> 00:34:23,110
-Talk properly.
-Yeah.

883
00:34:23,110 --> 00:34:24,440
So many people are watching.

884
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:25,320
Whatever issues we have,

885
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,360
we can talk back at home.

886
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,040
Let's talk properly.

887
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:28,040
Tell your mother

888
00:34:28,060 --> 00:34:29,710
to pack up and come home with me.

889
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:31,170
I'm here to bring you back.

890
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:33,070
Your grandmother has forgiven you.

891
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:33,870
That's right.

892
00:34:34,280 --> 00:34:35,000
Did you come all this way

893
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:35,880
to tell jokes?

894
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:38,030
What do you mean she forgave me?

895
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:39,560
I haven't forgiven her yet.

896
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:40,889
Didn't she tell you?

897
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:42,550
I will never go back to the Xia family.

898
00:34:42,550 --> 00:34:44,190
I won't let my mother go back either

899
00:34:44,190 --> 00:34:45,639
to continue being your slaves.

900
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:46,400
Hey, this kid...

901
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:47,199
Hey, Xiaolan.

902
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,510
How dare you speak like that?

903
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:49,030
You're just a youngster,

904
00:34:49,030 --> 00:34:50,000
and we three elders

905
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,230
can't even persuade you?

906
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:51,760
Xiaolan.

907
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:53,190
Listen to me.

908
00:34:53,590 --> 00:34:54,230
Come back home

909
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:56,280
and apologize properly
to your grandmother.

910
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:57,680
Then talk things through

911
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,800
with your sister Ziyu.

912
00:34:58,800 --> 00:34:59,400
Ziyu

913
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:00,230
will surely forgive you.

914
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:01,030
That's right.

915
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:02,760
We're all family.

916
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:05,550
Who's your family?

917
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:06,820
Let me say it again.

918
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:08,670
I will absolutely never

919
00:35:08,670 --> 00:35:09,760
return to the Xia family.

920
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,760
I won't let my mother go back either.

921
00:35:12,150 --> 00:35:13,400
The stigma between me and Zhang Erlai

922
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:15,190
has been cleared by my own efforts.

923
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:16,880
Zhang Erlai has been arrested.

924
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,550
As for what happened with that note,

925
00:35:18,550 --> 00:35:20,610
I believe the police will resolve it.

926
00:35:20,630 --> 00:35:21,590
Tell Xia Ziyu

927
00:35:22,150 --> 00:35:23,440
that although I haven't caught her

928
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:25,070
with evidence of her false accusations,

929
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:26,480
I will never let her off.

930
00:35:29,630 --> 00:35:30,630
Zhang Erlai was arrested?

931
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:32,690
I don't know. Haven't heard about it.

932
00:35:33,710 --> 00:35:35,550
This has nothing to do with our Ziyu...

933
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:36,840
Even if all men in the world

934
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:37,800
were to die...

935
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:38,800
Don't point your finger at me.

936
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:39,710
I would absolutely never

937
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:40,970
seduce Xia Ziyu's man.

938
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,030
You all know the truth

939
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:45,230
about what was going on between them.

940
00:35:45,230 --> 00:35:46,960
Don't try to put the blame on me.

941
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:49,000
And you,

942
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,000
Xia Dajun, right?

943
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,070
As my father,

944
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,800
you never once tried

945
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,860
to understand what really happened.

946
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:57,960
When rumors were

947
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,490
driving me to desperation,

948
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:01,810
did you feel even
a bit of sympathy for me?

949
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,970
After all this time,

950
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:04,210
did you ever think of

951
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:06,030
confronting Zhang Erlai
and settling the score with him?

952
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:07,630
No, you didn't, right?

953
00:36:08,110 --> 00:36:08,760
So tell me,

954
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,880
why should I go back to the Xia family?

955
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:12,250
Why should I go back to being treated
like a slave

956
00:36:12,250 --> 00:36:14,180
when I could live my life decently?

957
00:36:15,670 --> 00:36:17,440
Don't get physical. Stop it.

958
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:17,960
Don't get physical.

959
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,630
Let's talk this through.

960
00:36:18,630 --> 00:36:19,480
How could you speak

961
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,000
to your father like that?

962
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:20,760
Xiaolan. Xiaolan.

963
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:21,590
You've gone too far.

964
00:36:21,590 --> 00:36:22,360
We came here today

965
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,190
for another reason.

966
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,160
We need to see Liu Fen.

967
00:36:24,160 --> 00:36:25,190
Let's go. Take us to Liu Fen.

968
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:25,710
Let's go.

969
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:26,770
You must be joking.

970
00:36:27,030 --> 00:36:28,150
You think I'll do whatever you say?

971
00:36:28,150 --> 00:36:29,110
What's wrong with you?

972
00:36:29,110 --> 00:36:30,440
Where are your manners?

973
00:36:30,550 --> 00:36:31,420
No respect for your elders at all.

974
00:36:31,420 --> 00:36:32,680
Xia Dajun, look at this!

975
00:36:32,680 --> 00:36:34,010
Have you lost your mind?

976
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:35,230
We are all your elders.

977
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:37,070
How dare you speak to us like that?

978
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:37,920
Elders?

979
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:41,030
The elders

980
00:36:41,030 --> 00:36:41,850
who wish me dead?

981
00:36:41,850 --> 00:36:43,180
Hey, this kid is just...

982
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,590
She's speaking with absolutely no respect

983
00:36:44,590 --> 00:36:45,670
and no sense of propriety at all now.

984
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:46,670
If she were Ziyu,

985
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:47,920
I would have beaten her already,
I'm telling you.

986
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,480
Today, in front of everyone,

987
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,960
I'll make it clear to everyone

988
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:51,980
who your father is!

989
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:53,240
You ungrateful child!

990
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:55,230
You dare to hit your own father?

991
00:36:55,230 --> 00:36:55,910
Stop fighting!

992
00:36:55,910 --> 00:36:57,570
I'll teach you a lesson today!

993
00:37:00,510 --> 00:37:01,170
Uncle Yong!

994
00:37:01,670 --> 00:37:02,330
Uncle Yong!

995
00:37:03,710 --> 00:37:04,440
The Xia family...

996
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,480
Some people from the Xia family are here.

997
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,590
They're having a fight with Xiaolan.

998
00:37:06,590 --> 00:37:07,110
What?

999
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,000
I'll go check.

1000
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:08,540
No, don't!

1001
00:37:08,540 --> 00:37:09,540
Fen, listen to me.

1002
00:37:09,550 --> 00:37:10,480
Stay in the yard.

1003
00:37:10,710 --> 00:37:11,110
Qing,

1004
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:12,360
keep an eye on your aunts!

1005
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:12,840
No way.

1006
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:13,920
I need to help you.

1007
00:37:14,230 --> 00:37:15,150
Really, you can't.

1008
00:37:15,150 --> 00:37:15,610
This...

1009
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:18,000
Be careful!

1010
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:20,090
You don't deserve to be my father!

1011
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:22,350
Stop fighting! Stop!

1012
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:24,460
Everyone get out of my way!

1013
00:37:25,010 --> 00:37:25,850
Move!

1014
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:26,630
Yong is here! Yong is here!

1015
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:27,290
Step aside!

1016
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,000
We're family.

1017
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:34,940
Xiaolan's uncle! Xiaolan's uncle!

1018
00:37:34,940 --> 00:37:35,510
We're all family here.

1019
00:37:35,510 --> 00:37:36,510
You bastard!

1020
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,230
I didn't come to your village to
get even with you,

1021
00:37:38,230 --> 00:37:40,030
yet you dare come to our village?

1022
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,480
My sister marrying you was truly

1023
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:43,070
the worst luck imaginable!

1024
00:37:44,070 --> 00:37:44,670
Yong,

1025
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,710
let's talk this through.

1026
00:37:46,710 --> 00:37:47,510
Right, right.

1027
00:37:47,590 --> 00:37:49,120
I have nothing to say to you!

1028
00:37:51,110 --> 00:37:51,840
Xia Xiaolan,

1029
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:53,630
I'm asking you one last time!

1030
00:37:53,630 --> 00:37:55,490
Are you coming back with me or not?

1031
00:37:55,770 --> 00:37:56,190
You've never cared about me

1032
00:37:56,190 --> 00:37:57,720
as your daughter deep down.

1033
00:37:58,280 --> 00:38:00,190
If it weren't for my mom and my uncle,

1034
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:02,030
I would have died
in the Xia family long ago.

1035
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,760
Just pretend I'm already dead.

1036
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:05,030
I will absolutely never

1037
00:38:05,030 --> 00:38:05,510
return to the Xia family.

1038
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:06,800
Did you hear what Xiaolan said?

1039
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:07,800
Did you hear that?

1040
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,670
You dare come to our village
to take people away?

1041
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:11,000
You think Qijing Village has no one
to stand up for itself?

1042
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:11,440
Is that it?

1043
00:38:11,440 --> 00:38:11,980
That's right!

1044
00:38:11,980 --> 00:38:13,190
Who do you think you are?

1045
00:38:13,190 --> 00:38:14,400
Coming to our village causing trouble!

1046
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:14,840
Get out!

1047
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:17,800
Get out of here!

1048
00:38:18,230 --> 00:38:19,150
Who do you think you are?

1049
00:38:19,150 --> 00:38:20,230
Coming to cause trouble in our village!

1050
00:38:20,230 --> 00:38:20,840
Scram!

1051
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:22,510
If I ever come looking for you again,

1052
00:38:22,510 --> 00:38:23,840
I'm no better than a dog!

1053
00:38:23,930 --> 00:38:26,890
Get lost! Get lost already!

1054
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:28,180
Get far away from here!

1055
00:38:28,520 --> 00:38:29,150
What trash!

1056
00:38:29,150 --> 00:38:29,800
We should have cut ties with them
completely.

1057
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,460
Our Ziyu is just too kind-hearted.

1058
00:38:31,460 --> 00:38:31,990
Let's go.

1059
00:38:35,670 --> 00:38:36,280
Xiaolan.

1060
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,840
Go back and tell Xia Ziyu...

1061
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:39,210
-Let's talk properly.
-I know exactly what happened

1062
00:38:39,210 --> 00:38:40,860
between her and Wang Jianhua.

1063
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:41,710
I just don't want to

1064
00:38:41,710 --> 00:38:42,590
waste my time

1065
00:38:42,590 --> 00:38:43,630
on two worthless people.

1066
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:44,290
Yes, right.

1067
00:38:44,310 --> 00:38:45,190
If she wants to make it big,

1068
00:38:45,190 --> 00:38:46,250
I wish her success.

1069
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:47,400
Xiaolan, well...

1070
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:49,150
But if she ever dares to
act shamefully again,

1071
00:38:49,150 --> 00:38:50,210
I won't let her off.

1072
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,360
No, she won't.

1073
00:38:51,510 --> 00:38:52,000
And you.

1074
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:54,800
You were trying to help her stop me?

1075
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:55,510
Do you think if Xia Ziyu

1076
00:38:55,510 --> 00:38:56,630
becomes successful,

1077
00:38:56,630 --> 00:38:58,090
your family will benefit?

1078
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,690
You're just another blood bag.

1079
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,320
Without me and my mother,

1080
00:39:02,470 --> 00:39:03,330
all the bad stuff

1081
00:39:03,330 --> 00:39:04,590
will fall on your family.

1082
00:39:04,590 --> 00:39:05,480
W-What blood bag?

1083
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,360
Blood... Blood?

1084
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:07,190
Well, Xiaolan's uncle,

1085
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:08,360
please don't keep holding that stick.

1086
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:08,800
Yeah,

1087
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,800
it's quite scary.

1088
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:12,650
You're already scared?

1089
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:13,590
I'm not.

1090
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:14,880
In the future, that old hag

1091
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,550
will be depending on you two.

1092
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:17,760
Your good days

1093
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:19,020
are still ahead of you.

1094
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:19,590
Well,

1095
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:20,280
Xiaolan,

1096
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:21,510
no matter what,

1097
00:39:21,510 --> 00:39:22,640
I'm still your aunt,

1098
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:23,440
right?

1099
00:39:23,710 --> 00:39:25,690
We came here to talk things through
with you.

1100
00:39:25,690 --> 00:39:27,150
Yeah, we just wanted to
ask you to come back,

1101
00:39:27,150 --> 00:39:27,590
right?

1102
00:39:27,590 --> 00:39:29,590
Besides, our Ziyu is so kind.

1103
00:39:29,590 --> 00:39:31,370
She won't hold a grudge against you.

1104
00:39:31,370 --> 00:39:32,510
She's a college student after all.

1105
00:39:32,510 --> 00:39:32,910
Right.

1106
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:35,290
So she's a college student.
What's the big deal?

1107
00:39:35,290 --> 00:39:36,230
I'll get into college too

1108
00:39:36,230 --> 00:39:37,030
and show you.

1109
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:39,020
Alright, Xiaolan.

1110
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:40,280
Go ahead and take the exam.

1111
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:41,840
I believe you'll definitely pass.

1112
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:42,280
What a load of nonsense.

1113
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:42,730
After you pass,

1114
00:39:42,730 --> 00:39:43,590
this whole family will be yours.

1115
00:39:43,590 --> 00:39:44,850
Go away. Just get lost!

1116
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:46,510
What trash!

1117
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:47,710
Get lost! Leave now!

1118
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:53,960
As my father,

1119
00:39:54,710 --> 00:39:55,760
you never once tried

1120
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:57,820
to understand what really happened.

1121
00:39:58,030 --> 00:39:58,840
When rumors were

1122
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:00,370
making my life unbearable,

1123
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:02,710
did you feel even
a bit of sympathy for me?

1124
00:40:02,710 --> 00:40:03,840
After all this time,

1125
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:05,110
did you ever think of

1126
00:40:05,230 --> 00:40:08,430
confronting Zhang Erlai
and settling the score with him?

1127
00:40:13,490 --> 00:40:14,700
The rumor about Xiaolan

1128
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:15,830
dating Zhang Erlai—

1129
00:40:15,930 --> 00:40:17,190
where did it come from?

1130
00:40:18,190 --> 00:40:18,590
Well,

1131
00:40:18,960 --> 00:40:20,150
how would I know?

1132
00:40:20,680 --> 00:40:21,670
Someone said something,

1133
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:23,360
so the rumor started to spread.

1134
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,400
Besides, that Zhang Erlai

1135
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,870
admitted it himself, didn't he?

1136
00:40:25,870 --> 00:40:27,400
If he hadn't done anything,

1137
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:28,990
would he have confessed?

1138
00:40:29,070 --> 00:40:30,000
Sister-in-law,

1139
00:40:30,070 --> 00:40:31,920
let's not discuss this on the street.

1140
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:33,760
It's not something to be proud of.

1141
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:35,280
Let's talk back at home, Dajun.

1142
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:35,720
Hey,

1143
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,280
he asked me.

1144
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:38,500
I wasn't the one who spread it.

1145
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:40,630
And you're saying
I'm doing something shameful?

1146
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:41,880
When did I say anything?

1147
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:43,800
Didn't you just mention Zhang Erlai?

1148
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,400
Well, I...

1149
00:40:45,070 --> 00:40:45,590
Dajun,

1150
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:48,030
did you know Zhang Erlai was arrested?

1151
00:40:48,030 --> 00:40:49,160
He can't escape now.

1152
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:51,440
Did he implicate

1153
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:52,150
Xiaolan?

1154
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:54,280
The police won't arrest Xiaolan,
will they?

1155
00:40:54,280 --> 00:40:56,110
Zhang Erlai is charged with indecency.

1156
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,320
Why would the police arrest

1157
00:40:57,320 --> 00:40:58,190
the victim?

1158
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:00,710
Sister-in-law,

1159
00:41:00,710 --> 00:41:01,590
in these situations,

1160
00:41:01,590 --> 00:41:02,480
women always suffer the most.

1161
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:04,000
Why would they arrest Xiaolan?

1162
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,200
You're really funny.

1163
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,330
Isn't that what I just said?

1164
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:08,590
That women suffer?

1165
00:41:08,960 --> 00:41:09,960
Hey, you... Um...

1166
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,290
Dajun,

1167
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:13,230
I was just worried about

1168
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:14,110
our Xiaolan.

1169
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,150
Why are you giving me signals?

1170
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,590
Wait for me, Jingui!

1171
00:41:24,590 --> 00:41:25,190
Xiaolan.

1172
00:41:25,630 --> 00:41:26,850
Today, your father...

1173
00:41:26,850 --> 00:41:28,160
Don't worry, Mom.

1174
00:41:28,590 --> 00:41:29,320
Today, I embarrassed him

1175
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,070
in front of all those people

1176
00:41:30,070 --> 00:41:31,330
and made him lose face,

1177
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:32,750
and he also made a harsh threat,

1178
00:41:32,750 --> 00:41:34,070
saying he wouldn't come back again.

1179
00:41:34,070 --> 00:41:34,630
I think

1180
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:35,460
we can have a few days

1181
00:41:35,460 --> 00:41:36,260
of peace now.

1182
00:41:37,150 --> 00:41:37,550
But...

1183
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:38,610
Well...

1184
00:41:40,510 --> 00:41:41,040
Xiaolan,

1185
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:42,510
we can't keep going on like this.

1186
00:41:42,510 --> 00:41:43,910
What do you suggest we do?

1187
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,670
Go back and continue to work like
beasts of burden,

1188
00:41:45,670 --> 00:41:46,670
let them keep bullying us,

1189
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:47,190
spreading lies about me

1190
00:41:47,190 --> 00:41:48,230
and ruining my reputation?

1191
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:48,590
No.

1192
00:41:49,110 --> 00:41:50,590
That's not what I meant.

1193
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:52,840
I just feel that

1194
00:41:55,070 --> 00:41:56,230
I'm useless.

1195
00:41:57,150 --> 00:41:58,360
I failed protect you,

1196
00:41:59,160 --> 00:42:00,810
and I even make you

1197
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:02,370
worry about me all the time.

1198
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,400
I'm just so worthless.

1199
00:42:11,110 --> 00:42:11,630
Mom.

1200
00:42:12,510 --> 00:42:13,880
Stop overthinking it.

1201
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:15,600
The two of us

1202
00:42:15,630 --> 00:42:17,430
are depending on each other now.

1203
00:42:17,670 --> 00:42:19,270
No one is protecting anyone.

1204
00:42:19,630 --> 00:42:20,480
Besides,

1205
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,230
when I prepare for the exams later,

1206
00:42:22,230 --> 00:42:23,000
I'll need you

1207
00:42:23,030 --> 00:42:23,920
to support me.

1208
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:27,630
Xiaolan,

1209
00:42:29,510 --> 00:42:31,110
I just heard from your uncle
that you want to take

1210
00:42:31,110 --> 00:42:33,370
the college entrance exam. Is that true?

1211
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,320
Don't blame me

1212
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:37,720
for being discouraging.

1213
00:42:38,110 --> 00:42:38,840
College

1214
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:40,660
isn't easy to get into.

1215
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:42,680
That Chen Qing from the Chief's family,

1216
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:43,480
his academic performance

1217
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:44,430
is among the best

1218
00:42:44,590 --> 00:42:45,920
in our villages,

1219
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:48,010
yet he failed to
get into college last year.

1220
00:42:48,010 --> 00:42:48,550
And this year,

1221
00:42:48,550 --> 00:42:50,190
he's repeating at No.1 High School.

1222
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:52,590
Chen Qing happens to be
at No.1 High School?

1223
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:54,360
Then I'll ask him for information
tomorrow.

1224
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:54,880
Right.

1225
00:42:55,150 --> 00:42:55,750
You should

1226
00:42:55,880 --> 00:42:57,480
get more information first.

1227
00:42:57,760 --> 00:42:58,550
Don't rush.

1228
00:42:59,190 --> 00:42:59,550
Okay.

1229
00:43:00,670 --> 00:43:01,820
Fen, you've had a long day.

1230
00:43:01,820 --> 00:43:02,630
Get some rest.

1231
00:43:02,800 --> 00:43:03,400
All right.

1232
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:09,440
Cheng.

1233
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:10,110
Wei.

1234
00:43:10,280 --> 00:43:10,940
Zhou Cheng!

1235
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:12,690
There's a letter for you today.

1236
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:16,360
Thank you.

1237
00:43:17,030 --> 00:43:17,630
I'm leaving.

1238
00:43:17,630 --> 00:43:18,630
Be careful, Meng.

1239
00:43:19,670 --> 00:43:20,190
So?

1240
00:43:20,440 --> 00:43:21,400
Is it from Xiaolan?
